《'''印度的女兒'''》（{{lang-en|''India's Daughter''}}）是[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC）拍摄的一部[[纪录片|纪录片]]，为该电视台的系列节目「Storyville」當中的一集，讲述了[[印度黑公交轮奸案|2012年发生在印度德里的轮奸案]]。<ref name=SoulFilmMaker>{{cite news |title = Interview with Delhi gang rapist left 'stain on my soul', says British film maker |url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/11446337/Interview-with-Delhi-gang-rapist-left-stain-on-my-soul-says-British-film-maker.html |accessdate = 2015-03-06 |work = ''[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]'' |date = 2015-03-03 |archive-date = 2015-03-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150306062952/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/11446337/Interview-with-Delhi-gang-rapist-left-stain-on-my-soul-says-British-film-maker.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>在该事件中，一名23岁的女学生被六名男性轮姦并杀害。<ref name=YoutubeBlock /><ref name=IndiaBansTV>{{cite news |title=India bans TV stations from showing interview with man who raped student |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/03/india-outraged-interview-man-convicted-gang-rape-student |accessdate=2015-03-06 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2014-03-04 |archive-date=2021-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211015233907/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/03/india-outraged-interview-man-convicted-gang-rape-student }}</ref>

该纪录片原计划于3月8日[[国际妇女节|国际妇女节]]当日在全球播出。对于此影片的数条新闻被报道后，[[印度政府|印度政府]]撤销了该片在印度的播放许可。BBC遵从了印度当局的决定，最终该片没有在印度播出。该片亦被上传到视频分享网站[[YouTube|YouTube]]，随即在社交网站上大面积传播。3月5日，印度政府屏蔽了在YouTube上的该段视频。<ref name=YoutubeBlock>{{cite news |title = India asks YouTube to block banned rape film |url = https://news.yahoo.com/delhi-rape-victims-father-urges-viewing-documentary-080939613.html |accessdate = 2015-03-06 |work = [[Yahoo_News|Yahoo News]] |date = 2015-03-05 |archive-date = 2015-04-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402162209/https://news.yahoo.com/delhi-rape-victims-father-urges-viewing-documentary-080939613.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=YoutubeBlocks>{{cite news |title = YouTube blocks BBC's Nirbhaya documentary video |url = http://ibnlive.in.com/videos/532286/youtube-blocks-access-to-bbc-documentary-nirbhaya-in-india.html |accessdate = 2015-03-06 |work = [[India_Today|India Today]] |date = 2015-03-05 |archive-date = 2015-03-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150308091117/http://ibnlive.in.com/videos/532286/youtube-blocks-access-to-bbc-documentary-nirbhaya-in-india.html |dead-url = yes }}</ref>此纪录片以及印度政府的行为在全世界引起了广泛讨论。

==背景==
该影片讲述了2012年12月16日发生在南德里市的轮奸案。<ref name=Chaotic>{{cite news | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2258306/Delhi-gang-rape-Five-men-charged-Jyoti-Singh-Pandey-murder-appear-court.html | title=Judge bars Delhi gang rape defendants from chaotic courtroom after 150 people cram into space meant for 30 | work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]] | date=2013-01-07 | accessdate=2015-03-05 | last=Hills | first=Suzannah | archive-date=2014-01-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140118194133/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2258306/Delhi-gang-rape-Five-men-charged-Jyoti-Singh-Pandey-murder-appear-court.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>事件受害者乔蒂·辛格（Jyoti Singh）在与一位男性朋友看完电影《[[少年派的奇幻漂流_(电影)|少年派的奇幻漂流]]》后搭上了一辆私人运营的公交车回家。<ref name=tragedy>{{cite news| url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/exploring-the-lives-of-the-rape-victim-and-suspects-in-india-a-879187.html| title=Rape Tragedy in India: Dreams of 'the Fearless One'| work=Der Spiegel| date=2013-01-25| first1=Matthias| last1=Schulz| first2=Wieland| last2=Wagner| accessdate=2015-03-25| archive-date=2015-03-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150308205215/http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/exploring-the-lives-of-the-rape-victim-and-suspects-in-india-a-879187.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Rahman>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/03/india-outraged-interview-man-convicted-gang-rape-student|title=India bans TV stations from showing interview with man who raped student|work=The Guardian|date=2015-03-04|first=Maseeh|last=Rahman|accessdate=2015-03-25|archive-date=2021-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211015233907/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/03/india-outraged-interview-man-convicted-gang-rape-student}}</ref>她在车上被六人殴打和轮奸，她的朋友也受到了身体伤害，随后两人被扔下车。受害者乔蒂在被人发现后送往医院，她先在印度接受治疗，后来被转移到新加坡，最终在2012年12月29日死于印度
。<ref name=VicDies>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-20860569 | title=Delhi gang-rape victim dies in hospital in Singapore | work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] | date=2012-12-29 | accessdate=2015-03-05 | archive-date=2015-03-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150308234512/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-20860569 | dead-url=no }}</ref>该事件引起了媒体的广泛关注，激起了公众对印度政府没有提供对妇女足够保护的指责和抗议。<ref name=magnifies>{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/30/world/asia/weak-response-of-india-government-in-rape-case-stokes-rage.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 | title=<nowiki>Leaders’ Response Magnifies Outrage in India Rape Case</nowiki> | work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date=2012-12-29 | accessdate=2015-03-05 | last=Yardley | first=Jim | archive-date=2015-04-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402212908/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/30/world/asia/weak-response-of-india-government-in-rape-case-stokes-rage.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

国际媒体仅在抗议出现后才跟进报道。事件后六名男性被逮捕，包括一名为17岁的未成年人。其中一人在狱中死亡，死因可能为自杀，但他的亲属声称他是被谋杀的。<ref name=hanging>{{cite news | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/Suicide-or-murder-Nirbhaya-main-accused-found-hanging-in-Tihar/articleshow/18916760.cms?referral=PM | title=Suicide or murder? Nirbhaya main accused found hanging in Tihar | work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] | date=2013-03-12 | accessdate=2015-03-05 | last=Basu | first=Indrani | archive-date=2018-09-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915083737/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/Suicide-or-murder-Nirbhaya-main-accused-found-hanging-in-Tihar/articleshow/18916760.cms?referral=PM | dead-url=no }}</ref>四名男性被判有罪并被执行死刑，17岁的未成年人被判3年监禁。<ref name=Doubt>{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/09/14/world/asia/4-sentenced-to-death-in-rape-case-that-riveted-india.html?emc=edit_na_20130913 | title=Many Doubt Death Sentences Will Stem India Sexual Attacks | work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date=2013-09-13 | accessdate=2015-03-05 | last=Barry | first=Ellen | archive-date=2021-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304024636/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/09/14/world/asia/4-sentenced-to-death-in-rape-case-that-riveted-india.html?emc=edit_na_20130913 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=juvenile>{{cite news | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/Nirbhaya-gang-rape-case-Juvenile-found-guilty-of-rape-and-murder/articleshow/22183253.cms | title=Nirbhaya gang-rape case: Juvenile found guilty of rape and murder | work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] | date=2013-08-31 | accessdate=2015-03-05 | archive-date=2013-08-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130831170638/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/Nirbhaya-gang-rape-case-Juvenile-found-guilty-of-rape-and-murder/articleshow/22183253.cms | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==纪录片==
“印度的女儿”为BBC的系列节目“Storyville”中的一集，由莱斯里·奥德温（Leslee Udwin）执导。<ref name=SoulFilmMaker/>原计划本片在2015年3月8日国际妇女节当天在印度的[[NDTV_24x7|NDTV 24x7]]和[[英国|英国]]的[[BBC_Four|BBC Four]]播出。<ref name=clearance>{{cite news | url=http://www.ndtv.com/india-news/indias-daughter-required-clearances-were-taken-744072 | title=India's Daughter: Required Clearances Were Taken by Documentary Maker | work=[[NDTV|NDTV]] | date=2015-03-04 | accessdate=2015-03-04 | archive-date=2015-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150304105513/http://www.ndtv.com/india-news/indias-daughter-required-clearances-were-taken-744072 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Onsunday>{{cite news | url=http://www.media247.co.uk/bizasia/ndtv-24x7-to-air-nirbhaya-doc-on-sunday-2015 | title=<nowiki>NDTV 24×7 & BBC to air ‘Nirbhaya’ film on Sunday</nowiki> | work=[[NDTV_24x7|NDTV 24x7]] | date=2015-03-03 | accessdate=2015-03-04 | last=Baddhan | first=Raj | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150307223859/http://www.media247.co.uk/bizasia/ndtv-24x7-to-air-nirbhaya-doc-on-sunday-2015 | archivedate=2015年3月7日 }}</ref>2015年3月1日，影片制作者采访了关押在提哈尔监狱的一名凶手，随后印度媒体报道了此事。<ref name=PrisonInterview>{{cite news|title=Delhi bus rapist blames his victim in prison interview|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/11443462/Delhi-bus-rapist-blames-his-victim-in-prison-interview.html|accessdate=2015-03-06|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|date=2015-03-01|archive-date=2015-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150305095553/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/11443462/Delhi-bus-rapist-blames-his-victim-in-prison-interview.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ThisStory>{{cite news|title=This story must be told, says filmmaker who interviewed Dec 16 rapist|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/filmmaker-accused-of-giving-platform-to-rapist-after-interview-with-december-16-convict/article1-1322618.aspx|accessdate=2015-03-06|work=[[Hindustan_Times|Hindustan Times]]|date=2015-03-03|archive-date=2015-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150305164522/http://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/filmmaker-accused-of-giving-platform-to-rapist-after-interview-with-december-16-convict/article1-1322618.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=ThisStory /><ref name=DuringRape>{{cite news|title=During rape the girl shouldn't fight back, says December 16 convict|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/delhi-december-16-gang-rape-mukesh-singh-bbc-interview/1/421930.html|accessdate=2015-03-06|work=[[India_Today|India Today]]|date=2015-03-06|archive-date=2015-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150305162106/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/delhi-december-16-gang-rape-mukesh-singh-bbc-interview/1/421930.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年3月4日，印度政府下令禁止播出此片。BBC表示会遵守印度政府的决定不在印度播放此片。后来BBC将此片在英国的播放日期提前至4日。<ref name=BBCForward>{{cite news | url=http://www.theguardian.com/media/2015/mar/04/indias-daughter-bbc-delhi-rape-documentary-uk-india-ban | title=India’s Daughter: BBC brings forward airing of Delhi rape documentary | work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | date=2015-03-04 | accessdate=2015-03-05 | archive-date=2020-12-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202194350/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2015/mar/04/indias-daughter-bbc-delhi-rape-documentary-uk-india-ban | dead-url=no }}</ref>影片也被上传至YouTube，并在全球的社交网络上引起了广泛讨论。3月5日，印度政府要求屏蔽该影片，YouTube也遵守了印度方面的要求。<ref name=YoutubeBlock/><ref name=YoutubeBlocks/>

==采访==
其中一名凶手穆肯什·辛格（Mukesh Singh）在狱中接受了采访。他表示“当被强奸时，她不应该反抗。她应该安静地接受被强奸。这样他们在轮奸完她后便会扔下她去殴打那个男孩”。<ref name=EarlyBBC>{{cite news | url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/05/delhi-gang-rape-documentary-airs-early-on-bbc-following-objections | title=Delhi gang-rape documentary airs early on BBC following objections | work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | date=2015-03-05 | accessdate=2015-03-05 | last=Rawlinson | first=Kevin | archive-date=2015-03-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150307040959/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/05/delhi-gang-rape-documentary-airs-early-on-bbc-following-objections | dead-url=no }}</ref>他补充到：“对于强奸，女孩应该比男孩负更多责任，一名正派的女孩不会在晚上9点的时候在外面晃荡……女孩应该在家里做家务活，而不是穿着不合适的衣服在迪厅和酒吧里晃荡和做不合适的事。”<ref name=Rahman /> Navbharat时报称穆肯什因为这次采访收了40000[[卢比|卢比]]（合420英镑）。报道称他一开始要示200000卢比，后来双方商谈至40000卢比，这些钱最终给了穆肯什的家人。<ref name=paid>{{cite news |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-india-s-daughter-rape-convict-paid-rs40000-for-interview-2066496 |title=India's Daughter: Rape convict paid Rs.40,000 for interview? |author= |date=2015-03-06 |work=[[DNA_India|DNA India]] |6= |accessdate=2015-03-07 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108104354/https://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-india-s-daughter-rape-convict-paid-rs40000-for-interview-2066496 |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而影片制作者否认他们为这次采访给穆肯什钱。<ref name="isnot">{{cite news | url=http://www.thehindu.com/opinion/lead/indias-daughters-the-ban-that-actually-isnt/article6975342.ece | title=<nowiki>The ban that actually isn’t</nowiki> | work=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu]] | date=2015-03-10 | accessdate=2015-03-10 | author=Hegde, Sanjay | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108134454/https://www.thehindu.com/opinion/lead/indias-daughters-the-ban-that-actually-isnt/article6975342.ece | dead-url=no }}</ref>

A·P·辛格是该案件的一名辨护律师。他曾说：如果我的女儿或者姐妹因为婚前性行为蒙羞，我会把她带到我的农场，当着全家的面把她烧死。后来在被问及是否坚持这一立场时，他表示是的。<ref name="Independent">{{cite news | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/indias-daughter-how-india-tried-to-suppress-the-bbc-delhi-gangrape-documentary-10088890.html | title=India's Daughter: How India tried to suppress the BBC Delhi gang-rape documentary | work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] | date=2015-03-05 | accessdate=2015-03-05 | last=Withnall | first=Adam | archive-date=2015-09-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925184156/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/indias-daughter-how-india-tried-to-suppress-the-bbc-delhi-gangrape-documentary-10088890.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

